data.title: The Fat Duck, Bray, Berkshire
data.meta_description: The Fat Duck Restaurant, Heston Blumenthal, awarded three Michelin stars, restaurant of the year, Best Restaurant in the World and Best Restaurant in the UK.
data.text:
Experience the precision and invention of three-Michelin-star perfection

One of the fastest restaurants to ascend to three-star status, and once voted Best Restaurant by the World’s 50 Best, The Fat Duck is legendary for its exceptional creativity.

Each visit to The Fat Duck is an adventure full of unexpected flavour pairings, playful innovation and unique culinary creations.

Where will it take you?
